DOC = """
This suite executes LaCros-enabled version of performance CUJ (critical user
journey) test cases, to be run by partners (OEMs, ODMs) using Moblab.

@param build: The name of the image to test.
          Ex: x86-mario-release/R17-1412.33.0-a1-b29
@param board: The board to test on. Ex: x86-mario
@param pool: The pool of machines to utilize for scheduling. If pool=None
             board is used.
@param dry_run: simulate test execution without stressing the storage.
"""

